# Language Statistics
# Make Markdown detectable in GitHub language stats
*.md linguist-detectable

# Line Ending Normalization
* text=auto eol=lf

# Shell scripts (explicit LF)
*.sh text eol=lf

# Documentation & Config
*.md text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf

# Future binary assets
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.svg binary
